			<h1>Security Compliance Guidance</h1>
			<p class="tagline">Understanding New Zealand's Security Framework Requirements</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="compliance-content">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="intro">
				<p>Navigating New Zealand's security compliance landscape requires understanding key government frameworks. We help organizations comprehend these requirements and identify appropriate security solutions.</p>
			</div>

			<div class="framework-overview">
				<h2>Understanding Key Security Frameworks</h2>
				
				<div class="framework-item">
					<h3>NZISM (New Zealand Information Security Manual)</h3>
					<p>The government's comprehensive manual for protecting official information. It outlines security controls, risk management approaches, and technical requirements for government agencies and their partners.</p>
					<div class="our-role">
						<strong>Our Approach:</strong> We help interpret NZISM requirements and identify commercial solutions that align with its security objectives.
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="framework-item">
					<h3>Protective Security Requirements (PSR)</h3>
					<p>An all-of-government framework covering personnel, physical, and information security measures for protecting sensitive government information.</p>
					<div class="our-role">
						<strong>Our Approach:</strong> We provide guidance on PSR alignment and recommend security practices that support compliance objectives.
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="framework-item">
					<h3>International Security Standards</h3>
					<p>Various international standards and certifications recognized within New Zealand security frameworks, including FIPS 140-2, Common Criteria, and other validation programs.</p>
					<div class="our-role">
						<strong>Our Approach:</strong> We help identify products with relevant certifications that may support your security and compliance goals.
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="capabilities">
				<h2>How We Can Assist</h2>
				<div class="capability-grid">
					<div class="capability">
						<h3>Framework Education</h3>
						<p>Helping your team understand NZISM, PSR, and other relevant security requirements and how they apply to your organization.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="capability">
						<h3>Solution Identification</h3>
						<p>Recommending commercially available security products and solutions that align with framework requirements.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="capability">
						<h3>Implementation Support</h3>
						<p>Assisting with the deployment and configuration of security solutions in your environment.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="disclaimer-box">
				<h3>Important Information</h3>
				<p><strong>Hermetrix Technologies provides advisory services and implementation support for security solutions.</strong> We are not a government agency and cannot provide official compliance certifications or security clearances.</p>
				<p>Formal compliance status, security accreditations, and government approvals must be obtained through the appropriate official channels. We support your journey toward compliance through education and appropriate solution implementation.</p>
			</div>

			<div class="cta-section">
				<h2>Need to Understand Compliance Requirements?</h2>
				<p>Contact us to discuss how we can help your organization navigate security framework requirements.</p>
				<div class="contact-methods">
